org.apache.flex.compiler.common

Class PrefixMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flex.compiler.common.PrefixMap
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MutablePrefixMap

    public class PrefixMap
extends Object
implements Cloneable
    A PrefixMap contains a collection of prefix to namespace mappings found in MXML documents. This object is immutable. For a mutable version, look at MutablePrefixMap
